To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MoneyFlowIndex _mfi;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_mfi = MFI(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_mfi.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "positivemoneyflow", _mfi.PositiveMoneyFlow.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "negativemoneyflow", _mfi.NegativeMoneyFlow.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "previoustypicalprice", _mfi.PreviousTypicalPrice.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "moneyflowindex", _mfi.Current.Value);
}
